, left femur (LBA-XI-03). A, caudal view; B, cranial view. Abbreviations: cl, condylus lateralis; cm, condylus medialis; ct, crista trochanteris; faa, facies articularis antitrochanterica; fcd, facies caudalis; fcr, facies cranialis; fp, fossa poplitea; ii, incisura intercondylaris; licd, linea intermuscularis caudalis; licr, linea intermuscularis cranialis; pf, pneumatic foramen; sp, sulcus patellaris; tf, trochanter femoris; tfi, trochlea fibularis. Scale bar = 50 mm. Photographs by E. Kruidenier.
</paragraph>
